data.title: Full list of Australians recognised with Australia Day Honour
data.meta_description: Hundreds of Australians have been recognised with a 2024 Australia Day Honour.
data.text:
Hundreds of Australians have been recognised with a 2024 Australia Day Honour, including four who have been appointed the highest, AC, distinction. The Governor-General is pleased to announce the following appointments and awards:

Companion of the Order of Australia

Emeritus Professor David Vernon BOGER

Know the news with the 7NEWS app: Download today

For eminent service to chemical engineering as a scientist, academic and researcher, particularly in the field of non-Newtonian fluid mechanics, and to the environment.

Professor Deborah Jane TERRY
